Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many whole oranges are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many whole oranges are in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many half oranges are in the image?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many half oranges are in the image?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER2} == 1')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} == 1 and {ANSWER3} == 1')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
